item.title: High Signal P
item.description:
Overview

Since I got interested in ML, and technology in general, I’ve gathered some kind of mental list of people’s blogs I should check from time to time. I call these high signal people. But not only they share technical knowledge from ML or SWE, the blogs I enjoy the most are the ones that dig deep into whatever thing you consider normal. Take for example the article from Julian Schrittwieser on HDR photography. Is it related to his past work on Google Deepmind? No, he’s just playing and enjoying the tech we have right now. For someone like me who has just started his journey into tech these blogs are fascinating and I thank them very much for being this open and sharing cool stuff.
